1.)A pst file is a personal storage table. It's good to keep a record of things,
like emails, on a harddrive.
2.)The pffinfo program determines information about Personal Folder Files. The
pffexport program exports items stored in a Personal Folder File.
3.)You would use these programs to examine and look through emails.
4.)These programs help organize emails to look through them.
